These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-7-1::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: indie, rock, country, gospel, soul, blues, salsa
1. the fan of salsa is in the middle##1
2. the fan of indie is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3
3. the fan of country is somewhere between the fan of blues and the fan of salsa##7
4. the fan of rock is somewhere to the right of the fan of indie##5
5. the fan of soul is on the left of the fan of blues##1
6. the fan of indie is on the left of the fan of rock##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |   2    |    3    |   4    |    5    |     6     |  7   |
| Music-Genre   | soul | blues | country | salsa | indie | rock | gospel |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-7-2::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: disaster, drama, zombie, satire, superhero, spy, musical
 1. the person watching zombie movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching satire movies##5
 2. the person watching zombie movies is somewhere between the person watching musical movies and the person watching drama movies##7
 3. the person watching drama movies is on the left or right of the person watching superhero movies##3
 4. the person watching disaster movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching satire movies##5
 5. the person watching satire movies is somewhere between the person watching disaster movies and the person watching superhero movies##7
 6. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
 7. the person watching spy movies is on the left or right of the person watching satire movies##3
 8. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching satire movies##5
 9. the person watching superhero movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching drama movies##5
10. the person watching drama movies is on the left or right of the person watching superhero movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2       |    3     |    4    |      5      |     6      |   7    |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | zombie | superhero | drama | spy | satire | disaster |

