.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-7-3::.
The people use 7 different means of transport: jet-ski, ship, taxi, airplane, bus, skateboard, bike
1. the person driving the ship is somewhere between the person driving the jet-ski and the person driving the bus##7
2. the person driving the bus is somewhere between the person driving the taxi and the person driving the ship##7
3. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere to the left of the person driving the bus##5
4. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere between the person driving the bike and the person driving the jet-ski##7
5. the person driving the ship is somewhere to the right of the person driving the bus##5
6. the person driving the taxi is somewhere between the person driving the ship and the person driving the skateboard##7
7. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere to the left of the person driving the bus##5
8. the person driving the airplane is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1  |   2   |   3    |   4   |     5      |  6  |     7      |
| Transport   | bike | skateboard | taxi | bus | ship | jet-ski | airplane |

