4. the person driving the boat is somewhere to the left of the person driving the car##5
5. the person driving the car is between the person driving the airplane and the person driving the boat##2
6. the person driving the trike is somewhere to the left of the person driving the van##5
7. the person driving the boat is somewhere between the person driving the car and the person driving the trike##7
8. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
9. the person driving the van is somewhere to the right of the person driving the tram##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |  2   |   3   |  4   |  5   |     6     |    7    |
| Transport   | tram | trike | van | boat | car | airplane | jet-ski |

