.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-7-6::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: singing, rock-climbing, dancing, baking, drawing, collecting, filmmaking
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
2. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##5
4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3
5. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is drawing##3
6. the person who's hobby is dancing is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
7. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
8. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the far left or far right##3
9. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere between the person who's hobby is dancing and the person who's hobby is collecting##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |      3      |      4       |     5     |    6    |   7   |
| Hobby   | collecting | filmmaking | singing | drawing | baking | dancing | rock-climbing |

