 3. the owner of the fish is somewhere to the left of the owner of the cat##5
 4. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the owner of the goat##3
 5. the owner of the cat is somewhere between the owner of the chinchilla and the owner of the hamster##7
 6. the owner of the goat is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
 7. the owner of the rabbit is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the owner of the hamster is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
